    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284480/extras/35fa8fe18e29a4b7ea6784b2680d8b4a.poster.avif?t=1674106908\" width=600 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284480/extras/35fa8fe18e29a4b7ea6784b2680d8b4a.webm?t=1674106908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284480/extras/35fa8fe18e29a4b7ea6784b2680d8b4a.mp4?t=1674106908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Take on the ultimate adrenaline challenge with Soar, the realistic wingsuit game. Base jumping is known as the most dangerous recreation sport, but now you can experience the thrill without the risk. Soar through the mountains and maneuver through narrow canyons and over majestic peaks. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284480/extras/dbb5529d45e7f4b97ec5c7e5873a79a5.poster.avif?t=1674106908\" width=600 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284480/extras/dbb5529d45e7f4b97ec5c7e5873a79a5.webm?t=1674106908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284480/extras/dbb5529d45e7f4b97ec5c7e5873a79a5.mp4?t=1674106908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game features realistic physics, beautiful graphics, and challenging courses that will keep you coming back for more. Take the leap and join the ultimate base jumping experience with Soar, the safest way to satisfy your thirst for adventure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284480/extras/2bd08c68fbc84e28b5275da6808b060c.poster.avif?t=1674106908\" width=600 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284480/extras/2bd08c68fbc84e28b5275da6808b060c.webm?t=1674106908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284480/extras/2bd08c68fbc84e28b5275da6808b060c.mp4?t=1674106908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Soar it's still early in development, so expect full list of game modes at later date. Meanwhile, feel free to wishlist and connect with us!</strong>",
